      {
        "id": "comment-intro",
        "type": "nodetool.workflows.base_node.Comment",
        "data": {
          "comment": "# 🎓 Learning Path Generator\n\nName a topic and a research agent searches the web to build a structured, module-by-module study plan.\n\n**Pipeline:** Topic → build prompt → Research agent (search + browse) → format as markdown\n\n**Try this:** change the topic, or edit the prompt to set the number of modules or difficulty. Pick a model on the agent first."
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "selected": false,
          "position": {
            "x": 0,
            "y": -220
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 460,
          "height": 180,
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {},
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "2",
        "type": "nodetool.text.Prompt",
        "data": {
          "prompt": "\n# Learning path: {{ topic }}\n\n## Overview\n{{ overview }}\n\n{% for m in modules %}\n### {{ m.title }}\n{{ m.description }}\n\nResources:\n{% for r in m.resources %}\n- {{ r }}\n{% endfor %}\n\n{% endfor %}\n"
        },
        "ui_properties": {
          "position": {
            "x": 1280,
            "y": 465
          },
          "zIndex": 0,
          "width": 280,
          "selectable": true,
          "bypassed": false,
          "title": "4️⃣ Format as markdown"
        },
        "dynamic_properties": {
          "topic": null,
          "overview": null,
          "modules": null
        },
        "dynamic_outputs": {}
      },
      {
        "id": "3",
        "type": "nodetool.agents.Agent",
        "data": {
          "model": {
            "type": "language_model",
            "provider": "openai",
            "id": "gpt-5-mini",
            "name": "GPT-5 mini",
            "path": null,
            "supported_tasks": []
          },
          "tools": [
            {
              "type": "tool_name",
              "name": "google_search"
            },
            {
              "type": "tool_name",
              "name": "browser"
            }
          ],
          "max_tokens": 100000,
          "system": "You are a research assistant.\n\nGoal\n- Conduct thorough research on the given objective\n- Use tools to gather information from multiple sources\n- Synthesize information into the structured output format specified\n\nTools Available\n- google_search: Search the web for information\n- browser: Navigate to URLs and extract content\n\nWorkflow\n1. Break down the research objective into specific queries\n2. Use google_search to find relevant sources\n3. Use browser to extract content from promising URLs\n4. Synthesize all findings into the requested output format\n\nOutput Format\n- Return a structured JSON object matching the defined output schema\n- Be thorough and cite sources where appropriate\n- Ensure all required fields are populated with accurate information\n",
          "mode": "plan"
        },
